<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>CliniCare Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #f2f4f8;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    .app {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
      position: relative;
    }

    .sidebar {
      width: 210px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #3559c7 0%, #2b49a8 100%);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 10px 18px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      padding: 6px 8px;
    }

    .logo-icon {
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #3559c7;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .menu {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .menu li a {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #dbe7ff;
      padding: 12px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .menu li a:hover,
    .menu li a.active {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .logout {
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .logout a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #dbe7ff;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .logout a:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .main {
      flex: 1;
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .topbar {
      height: 56px;
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d8dde6;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 0 28px;
    }

    .search-box {
      width: 290px;
      height: 34px;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .search-box input {
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      background: transparent;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .user-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 24px 34px;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .add-btn {
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 18px;
      background: #3559c7;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      font-size: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(53, 89, 199, 0.25);
    }

    .add-btn:hover {
      background: #2f4fb5;
    }

    .add-icon {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-top: -1px;
    }

    .cards {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #e7ebf2;
      padding: 26px;
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .appointment-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .appointment-item {
      border: 1px solid #edf0f5;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 22px 18px;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #1f2937;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .empty-box {
      min-height: 170px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      color: #7b8495;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .chat-widget {
      position: fixed;
      right: 22px;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 470px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 28px 28px 0 0;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .chat-header {
      height: 58px;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d9dce2;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 16px;
    }

    .chat-brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .chat-brand-icon {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 11px;
      background: #3559c7;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .chat-user {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .chat-body {
      padding: 12px 14px 0;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .chat-inner {
      border: 5px solid #2d86dc;
      border-bottom-width: 4px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 18px 16px 8px;
      min-height: 430px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .bot-message {
      background: #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px 20px 16px;
      width: 92%;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .message-time {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #8a8f99;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .suggest-title-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin: 10px 2px 10px;
    }

    .suggest-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4b5563;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .suggest-line {
      width: 32px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 99px;
    }

    .suggest-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .suggest-item {
      background: #d9d9d9;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 14px;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 11px 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #3f3f46;
    }

    .suggest-item:hover {
      background: #cfd3d8;
    }

    .chat-input-wrap {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .chat-input {
      flex: 1;
      height: 34px;
      border: 1px solid #cfd5df;
      border-radius: 11px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      outline: none;
    }

    .send-btn {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #d1d5db;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .send-btn:hover {
      background: #c4c9d1;
    }

    .chat-note {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #7c8391;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1200px) {
      .chat-widget {
        width: 400px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .sidebar {
        display: none;
      }

      .main {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .chat-widget {
        position: static;
        width: calc(100% - 40px);
        margin: 20px auto 0;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      .hero {
        text-align: left;
      }

      .add-btn {
        position: static;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }

      .cards {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div>
        <div class="logo">
          <div class="logo-icon">+</div>
          <div class="logo-text">CliniCare</div>
        </div>

        <ul class="menu">
          <li><a href="#" class="active">Trang chủ</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Quản lý lịch hẹn</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Quản lý khoa và bác sĩ</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Quản lý chat bot</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Cài đặt</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="logout">
        <a href="#">Đăng xuất</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="main">
      <div class="topbar">
        <div class="search-box">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7" stroke="#6b7280" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="20" x2="16.5" y2="16.5" stroke="#6b7280" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
          <input type="text" placeholder="Tìm kiếm bác sĩ, chuyên khoa..." />
        </div>
        <div class="user-name">Nguyễn Gia Huy</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="hero">
          <h1>Xin chào, Abc</h1>
          <p>Tổng quan sức khỏe của bạn</p>

          <button class="add-btn">
            <span class="add-icon">+</span>
            <span>Thêm lịch hẹn</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card">
            <h2>Lịch hẹn hôm nay</h2>
            <div class="appointment-list">
              <div class="appointment-item">09:00 – Bác sĩ Minh (Tim mạch)</div>
              <div class="appointment-item">10:30 – Bác sĩ Lan (Da liễu)</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2>Lịch đã hủy hôm nay</h2>
            <div class="empty-box">Không có lịch nào bị hủy</div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2>Lịch hẹn sắp tới</h2>
            <div class="appointment-list">
              <div class="appointment-item">Ngày mai – 14:00 – Bác sĩ Nam</div>
              <div class="appointment-item">25/03 – 09:00 – Bác sĩ Hương</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <section class="chat-widget">
      <div class="chat-header">
        <div class="chat-brand">
          <div class="chat-brand-icon">+</div>
          <span>CliniCare</span>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-user">Nguyễn Gia Huy</div>
      </div>

      <div class="chat-body">
        <div class="chat-inner">
          <div>
            <div class="bot-message">
              Xin chào Tôi là AI hỗ trợ y tế. Bạn đang gặp vấn đề gì?
              <div class="message-time">12:40 PM</div>
            </div>

            <div class="suggest-title-row">
              <div class="suggest-title">Câu hỏi gợi ý</div>
              <div class="suggest-line"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="suggest-list">
              <button class="suggest-item">Tôi bị đau đầu thường xuyên</button>
              <button class="suggest-item">Triệu chứng của bệnh sốt xuất huyết là gì?</button>
              <button class="suggest-item">Tôi cần khám bác sĩ dị ứng da nào?</button>
              <button class="suggest-item">Liên tục khó thở ngực nên cần làm gì?</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="chat-input-wrap">
              <input
                id="chatInput"
                class="chat-input"
                type="text"
                placeholder="Mô tả triệu chứng của bạn ..."
              />
              <button class="send-btn" onclick="sendMessage()">➤</button>
            </div>

            <div class="chat-note">
              ⚠ Đây là tư vấn sơ bộ. Vui lòng khám bác sĩ để chẩn đoán chính xác.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
